#  - physics tuning applied by car.gd — engine/reverse force is newtons per
#    traction wheel (Godot drives all four, so thrust is 4x), speeds in m/s,
#    grip is VehicleWheel3D friction_slip (rear kept slightly above front:
#    mild understeer is more forgiving than snap oversteer)
#  - "body" picks the CarBody builder for the 3D look
#  - "profile" is the side-view outline polygon for the menu preview
#    (metres, +y up, nose toward -x); wheels are drawn from wheel_z/radius
